<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    @page { margin: 0; }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: DejaVu Sans, sans-serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #1a1f2e;
      font-size: 11pt;
    }

    /* ── Gold top bar ── */
    .top-bar {
      background: #ffbe33;
      height: 8px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* ── Header ── */
    .header {
      background: #1a1f2e;
      padding: 28px 48px 22px;
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .header-left  { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; }
    .header-right { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right; width: 200px; }

    .brand {
      font-family: DejaVu Sans, sans-serif;
      font-size: 22pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffbe33;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }
    .brand-tagline {
      font-size: 7.5pt;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .header-badge {
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,190,51,0.4);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header-badge div:first-child {
      font-size: 7pt;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }
    .header-badge div:last-child {
      font-size: 9pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffbe33;
      margin-top: 3px;
    }

    /* ── Page body ── */
    .page-body { padding: 36px 48px 20px; }

    /* ── Certificate title block ── */
    .cert-title-block { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .cert-seal {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #ffbe33;
      margin: 0 auto 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .cert-seal-inner {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #ffbe33;
      border: 3px solid #1a1f2e;
      margin: 0 auto 14px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 58px;
      font-size: 24pt;
    }
    .cert-main-title {
      font-size: 20pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1f2e;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .cert-subtitle {
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }
    .cert-title-divider {
      width: 60px;
      height: 3px;
      background: #ffbe33;
      margin: 12px auto 0;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    /* ── Proof banner ── */
    .proof-banner {
      background: rgba(16,185,129,0.08);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.35);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .proof-banner-title {
      font-size: 10.5pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #065f46;
    }
    .proof-banner-sub {
      font-size: 8.5pt;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-top: 3px;
    }

    /* ── Section cards ── */
    .section-grid {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: separate;
      border-spacing: 10px 0;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .section-cell { display: table-cell; vertical-align: top; width: 50%; }

    .info-card {
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .info-card-header {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 9px 16px;
      font-size: 7.5pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .info-card-header .accent { color: #ffbe33; margin-right: 5px; }
    .info-card-body { padding: 12px 16px; }

    .info-row {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 5px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
      font-size: 9pt;
    }
    .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .info-label { display: table-cell; color: #9ca3af; width: 46%; vertical-align: top; }
    .info-value { display: table-cell; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1f2e; vertical-align: top; }
    .info-value.highlight { color: #ffbe33; }
    .info-value.green { color: #059669; }

    /* ── Full-width card ── */
    .full-card {
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .full-card-header {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 9px 18px;
      font-size: 7.5pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .full-card-body {
      padding: 14px 18px;
    }
    .ref-box {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
    }
    .ref-number {
      font-size: 18pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1f2e;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .ref-sub {
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-top: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    /* ── Status badge ── */
    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(16,185,129,0.12);
      color: #065f46;
      border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.35);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      font-size: 9pt;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* ── Legal note ── */
    .legal-box {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-left: 3px solid #ffbe33;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: #6b7280;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .legal-box strong { color: #1a1f2e; }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer {
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 14px 48px;
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
      background: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .footer-left  { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 7.5pt; color: #9ca3af; }
    .footer-right { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right; width: 40%; font-size: 7.5pt; color: #9ca3af; }
    .footer-brand { font-weight: 700; color: #ffbe33; }

    /* ── Bottom gold bar ── */
    .bottom-bar {
      background: #1a1f2e;
      height: 5px;
      width: 100%;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top-bar"></div>

<!-- Header -->
<div class="header">
  <div class="header-left">
    <div class="brand">BizHub</div>
    <div class="brand-tagline">Plateforme d'investissement &amp; startup</div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-right">
    <div class="header-badge">
      <div>Numéro de certificat</div>
      <div>CERT-{{ deal.deal_id }}-{{ date|date('Ymd') }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Body -->
<div class="page-body">

  <!-- Certificate title -->
  <div class="cert-title-block">
    <div class="cert-seal-inner">&#10003;</div>
    <div class="cert-main-title">Certificat de Signature</div>
    <div class="cert-subtitle">Preuve de signature électronique</div>
    <div class="cert-title-divider"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Proof banner -->
  <div class="proof-banner">
    <div class="proof-banner-title">
      &#10003; &nbsp;Le présent document atteste que le contrat d'investissement a été signé électroniquement
    </div>
    <div class="proof-banner-sub">
      Signature enregistrée le {{ signed_at|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }} — Plateforme BizHub
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Deal reference (full width) -->
  <div class="full-card">
    <div class="full-card-header">&#9632; &nbsp;Référence du deal</div>
    <div class="full-card-body">
      <div class="ref-box">
        <div class="ref-number">DEAL-{{ deal.deal_id }}</div>
        <div class="ref-sub">Identifiant unique de la transaction BizHub</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:table;width:100%;margin-top:8px;">
        <div style="display:table-cell;text-align:center;padding:0 10px;border-right:1px solid #e5e7eb;">
          <div style="font-size:8pt;color:#9ca3af;margin-bottom:2px;">Montant</div>
          <div style="font-size:13pt;font-weight:700;color:#ffbe33;">{{ deal.amount|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} TND</div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:table-cell;text-align:center;padding:0 10px;border-right:1px solid #e5e7eb;">
          <div style="font-size:8pt;color:#9ca3af;margin-bottom:2px;">Statut final</div>
          <span class="status-badge">&#10003; {{ status_label }}</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:table-cell;text-align:center;padding:0 10px;">
          <div style="font-size:8pt;color:#9ca3af;margin-bottom:2px;">Date de création</div>
          <div style="font-size:9pt;font-weight:700;color:#1a1f2e;">{{ deal.created_at ? deal.created_at|date('d/m/Y') : '—' }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Parties grid -->
  <div class="section-grid">
    <!-- Signataire (investisseur) -->
    <div class="section-cell">
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-header"><span class="accent">&#9632;</span> Signataire — Investisseur</div>
        <div class="info-card-body">
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Nom complet</div>
            <div class="info-value">{{ buyer.fullName ?? '—' }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Email</div>
            <div class="info-value" style="font-size:8.5pt;">{{ buyer.email ?? '—' }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Rôle</div>
            <div class="info-value">Investisseur</div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Date signature</div>
            <div class="info-value green">{{ signed_at|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Startup (vendeur) -->
    <div class="section-cell">
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-header"><span class="accent">&#9632;</span> Startup — Bénéficiaire</div>
        <div class="info-card-body">
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Nom complet</div>
            <div class="info-value">{{ seller.fullName ?? '—' }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Email</div>
            <div class="info-value" style="font-size:8.5pt;">{{ seller.email ?? '—' }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Rôle</div>
            <div class="info-value">Startup / Porteur de projet</div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Plateforme</div>
            <div class="info-value">BizHub</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Signature method -->
  <div class="full-card">
    <div class="full-card-header">&#9632; &nbsp;Méthode de signature</div>
    <div class="full-card-body">
      <div style="display:table;width:100%;">
        <div style="display:table-cell;vertical-align:top;width:50%;padding-right:14px;">
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Méthode</div>
            <div class="info-value">
              {% if deal.yousign_signature_request_id %}
                Signature électronique (Yousign v3)
              {% else %}
                Signature électronique (lien sécurisé)
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Niveau</div>
            <div class="info-value">Signature électronique avancée</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:table-cell;vertical-align:top;width:50%;padding-left:14px;border-left:1px solid #e5e7eb;">
          {% if deal.yousign_signature_request_id %}
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">ID Yousign</div>
            <div class="info-value" style="font-size:7.5pt;word-break:break-all;">{{ deal.yousign_signature_request_id }}</div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Statut Yousign</div>
            <div class="info-value green">
              {{ deal.yousign_status == 'done' ? '&#10003; Complété' : (deal.yousign_status ?? 'Signé') }}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Legal note -->
  <div class="legal-box">
    <strong>Valeur juridique :</strong> Ce certificat constitue la preuve de la conclusion d'un accord d'investissement entre
    les parties susmentionnées sur la plateforme BizHub. Le contrat original signé fait foi entre les parties.
    Ce document a été généré automatiquement le <strong>{{ date|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</strong> par la plateforme BizHub.
    Toute falsification de ce document est passible de poursuites pénales conformément à la législation en vigueur.
  </div>

</div>

<!-- Footer -->
<div class="footer">
  <div class="footer-left">
    <span class="footer-brand">BizHub</span> — Plateforme d'investissement &amp; startup<br>
    Émis le {{ date|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }} &mdash; Certificat n° CERT-{{ deal.deal_id }}-{{ date|date('Ymd') }}
  </div>
  <div class="footer-right">
    Ce document est généré automatiquement.<br>
    Authentique et non modifiable.
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bottom-bar"></div>

</body>
</html>
